<template>
    <el-table 
            :data='tabelaData'
            stripe
            :default-sort='{ prop: "date", order: "descending" }'
            style='width: 100%'
            ref='multipleTable'>

            <el-table-column 
                prop='nomeProduto'
                label='Produto'
                width='135'>
            </el-table-column>

    </el-table>

</template>
    
<script>
export default {
    name: 'TabelaProdutos',
    props: {
        tabelaData: {
            type: Array,
            required: true
        },
        paginacao: {
            type: Object,
            required: true
        }
    },
    data() {
        return {};
    },
    methods: {
    }
};
</script>
<style lang="scss">
#tabela-gestao-contrato-originacao {

    .el-table {
        border-top-right-radius: 11px;
        border-top-left-radius: 11px;
    }
    .status-processamento {
        max-width: 148px;
        word-break: break-word;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 17px;
    }
    .tabela-gestao-contrato-originacao__paginacao {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        background: var(--white);
        padding: 14px 11px;
        border-bottom-left-radius: 11px;
        border-bottom-right-radius: 11px;

        .pagina {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-weight: 600;
        }
    }
    .tabela-gestao-icone {
        i {
            font-size: 27px;
        }
    }
}
</style>
